<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When using prepared statements I bind dates into the query.</p>

<p>for example:</p>

<p>$query = $this-&gt;db-&gt;query("select * from table where DATE( ? ) between from and to", array($date));</p>

<p>if $date is "2009-06-04" it works fine:  DATE( "2009-06-04" )</p>

<p>But when $date contains "now()" the quotes should be left out:  DATE( now() ).</p>

<p>It's not a big deal. But it makes my life a bit easier :-)</p>

